lets simulate something

sim_mean_sd = function(n, mu = 2, sigma = 3) {
  
  sim_data = tibble(
    x = rnorm(n, mean = mu, sd = sigma),
  )
  
  sim_data %>% 
    summarize(
      mu_hat = mean(x),
      sigma_hat = sd(x)
    )
}

simulate by running:

sim_mean_sd(30)
## # A tibble: 1 x 2
##   mu_hat sigma_hat
##    <dbl>     <dbl>
## 1   1.99      2.79
